entries.journal_entry_description: Find the Pressurized Liquid Storage Unit and remove the Flow Control Valves
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Remove the Flow Control Valves from the Pressurized Liquid Storage Unit
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Those are all the valves I need. Come back and replace the ones on the Sedimentation Tank.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Replace the worn valves on the Sedimentation Tank with the new ones
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Phor Cl-lan to see if anything else needs to be done to get clean water.
